{"tid":2461605,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"鮑威爾：隨著經濟復蘇　聯儲局將減少買債","createTime":"2021-03-25T13:02:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T13:44:24.000Z","uid":187876,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"d3819de785076cbd65a05f079395e4200e69fa1a","tid":2461605,"uid":187876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T13:02:18.000Z","msg":"美國聯儲局主席鮑威爾表示，隨著經濟復蘇和目標取得實質性進展，聯儲局將減少買債；當經濟幾乎完全復蘇時才會考慮加息。<br />\n<br />\n他在接受美國全國公共廣播電台專訪時表示，當局上調對美國的經濟預測，是反映疫苗進展和財政援助，聯儲局會致力維持平均2%的通脹。<br />\n<br />\n他指，目前聯儲局政策的任何改變，都將是緩慢而極度透明，而且只會在美國經濟更力完全復蘇後才會進行。<br />\n<br />\n鮑威爾又表示，目前的債務水位無法持續，但美國現時有能力還債。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1582607-20210325.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1582607-20210325.htm&d=Vr1Lb3BWhK3V%2BSmIqtN%2B%2FopVoCVS%2BR9CeaLj%2Fs3YFXo%3D&h=79d2d181\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1582607-20210325.htm&h=583b7f9d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1582607-20210325.htm</a>"},{"pid":"c474c3a02271f881692c787578470b9dce20ff98","tid":2461605,"uid":84926,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T13:03:37.000Z","msg":"熊市來了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e12a19652cc1c73ab0bc91311b9f24146c5b89a3","tid":2461605,"uid":333199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T13:06:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5864dfdb9dfc25c26ec9e55d4a5e5c02e06d1cd9","tid":2461605,"uid":283222,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T13:07:03.000Z","msg":"債色又可再衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img 